high_descs: Turn around and face the desk behind you.
Pick up the CD that's directly to the left of the small clock.
Move back a step with the CD, so you have enough space to open a desk drawer.
Open the bottom drawer and place the CD in the front left corner, and then close the drawer.
Step back closer to the desk again.
Pick up the remaining CD from the desk.
Move back once again away from the desk, so you have room to open a drawer.
Open the bottom desk drawer and place the CD inside behind the one you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two CDs to the bottom drawer of the desk.
